messages.content: Я — большая языковая модель, разработанная Google. Чем я могу вам помочь?

thoughts.subject: Understanding the Inquiry's Intent
thoughts.description: I'm focused on the user's question, trying to parse its underlying intent. It seems like they're trying to figure out the model type, which, as I understand, isn't something I can disclose. I'm preparing an explanation about my nature as a Google-trained language model, which I think will be a satisfactory response.
